I've been wanting to do this for some time, and I was surprised how easy it was.<br><br>There are four merchant factions in Shadow Haven, corresponding to the four quadrants of the city. Each faction can be raised by a quest that needs to be done no more than a half dozen times to raise each faction level. I was mostly interested in just being able to buy and sell, so I did most of them only a few times. Some of the quests raise faction for more than one quadrant, but only raise one of them significantly, so you have to identify the main one to do it efficiently. Best of all, none of these quests lower any factions.<br><br>Here are the quests for each one:<br><br>House of Fordel – southeast quadrant, mostly human<br><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/quest.html?quest=1534">Steaton’s Deliveries</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> – Take an item to the Bazaar and bring another one back. Starts at (265, 1575)<br><br>House of Midst – northeast quadrant, mostly erudite<br><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/quest.html?quest=1453">Beriol’s Research</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> – Take an item to Katta. My faction is bad in Katta, so I didn’t do this one. Starts in the library, near (1400, -420).<br><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/quest.html?quest=1538">The Pulsating Rock</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> – Kill mud burrowers in Paludal for pulsating rocks. They drop about every 4 or 5 kills. Easy for anyone over level 10. Just need invis to get past the humans near the zone. Starts in the library, near (1400, -420)<br><br>House of Stout – southwest quadrant, mostly dwarf and gnome<br><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/quest.html?quest=1661">Zimloro’s Potion Quest</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> – Deliver an item to Shadeweaver Thicket and bring another one back. Need invis to get through Paludal, unless you’re over level 20. Starts near (-420, 1425).<br><br>Traders of the Haven – northwest quadrant, mostly human<br><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/quest.html?quest=1449">Traders of the Haven Quest</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> – Deliver an item to the Bazaar, back to Shadow Haven, then to Fungus Grove and back to Shadow Haven. Starts near (-400, 400)<br> <p><br>Heilig Hangranate<br>Level 55 murderous, suicidal battlecleric<br><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=93838>My Magelo Profile</a></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub17.ezboard.com/uheilighangranate.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Heilig Hangranate</A> at: 4/1/02 12:15:43 pm<br></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub17.ezboard.com/fforlornheroes64817frm4.showNextMessage?topicID=26.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub17.ezboard.com/fforlornheroes64817frm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=26.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/egyptian/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub17.ezboard.com/fforlornheroes64817frm4.emailToFriend?topicID=26.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub17.ezboard.com/fforlornheroes64817frm4.threadControl?topicID=26.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub17.ezboard.com/fforlornheroes64817frm4.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=26.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub17.ezboard.com/fforlornheroes64817frm4.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=26.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"